description.narrative: Strong technical guidance and quality assurance improved programme planning, evidence generation, monitoring, implementing partners and contribution management as well as reporting. The evidence base decision making has been improved through the Data for children platform, the Iterative Beneficiary Monitoring and the Unified monitoring. Strong and active engagement with donors and partners, along with timely submission of all donor reports, strengthened the contribution management function, leading to better funds allocation and financial implementation and monitoring. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:19/01/2022
